data.description: This charming 2 bedroom, 1 bath ranch home is an absolute gem offering a cozy and comfortable living space with a range of delightful features. Under cabinet lighting, newer counters with breakfast bar, and tankless water heater. The large, fully-fenced backyard is your private oasis. The deck and patio offer excellent outdoor spaces to relax, dine, and entertain. The storage shed is a practical addition that helps keep your home clutter-free. Two pergolas in the backyard add a touch of elegance and provide shade for those hot summer days. An excellent opportunity to own a property that offers a warm and welcoming atmosphere, a spacious backyard for outdoor activities, and all the features you need for a comfortable, convenient lifestyle. Don't miss your chance to make this delightful house your new home! Roof approx. 6 years, Furnace and A/C approx. 12 years, Water Heater 2022, newer gutters and several windows newer Buyer got "cold feet" prior to doing an inspection. It's your lucky day!
